338
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:12,910
Sorry.

339
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,450
You can't bring the bag.

340
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,550
It's the first time I've seen

341
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:54,750
