346
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:31,950
They were stolen from
Zi Mausoleum and Du Mausoleum.

347
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:33,800
Many treasures were taken.

348
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,880
Please wait for a moment.

349
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:45,400
Captain Qi.

350
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:45,880
Please wait.

351
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,920
Those are either
from Zi Mausoleum or Du Mausoleum.

352
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:48,580
Don't go in.

353
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,330
What are you doing?

354
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:55,720
The black pottery figurines are either
from Zi Mausoleum or Du Mausoleum.

355
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:57,880
Go on.

356
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,960
The thermoluminescence
testing results show

357
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:04,150
that the male figurine
is from the Western Jin,

358
00:18:04,150 --> 00:18:06,040
