359
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:06,680
These errors

360
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:08,740
are likely because they were burned.

361
00:18:09,490 --> 00:18:10,200
There must have been a fire

362
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:12,130
in the tomb during the Western Jin.

363
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:14,290
I read a paper before,

364
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,400
it mentioned that during the Western Jin,

365
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:19,130
