Suo Chen in Book of Jin.

373
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,110
It says that at the end of Western Jin,

374
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:32,000
there was constant warfare.

375
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:34,200
Hungry people in Chang'an

376
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:36,750
were stolen from
Zi Mausoleum and Du Mausoleum.

377
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:38,280
