380
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,110
These black pottery figurines

381
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:46,480
were likely stolen from these two tombs.

382
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:49,110
Based on that,

383
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:51,920
