384
00:18:52,690 --> 00:18:53,970
At first, I didn't know

385
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,160
why they were black.

386
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,440
Then I got closer and thought,

387
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:59,280
why is this female figurine's

388
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,760
color so uneven?

389
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:02,070
It seems like
there's some colored painting.

390
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:03,270
At that moment, I thought

391
00:19:03,270 --> 00:19:04,400
maybe it was burned.

392
00:19:04,620 --> 00:19:05,830
So I wiped it with a glove,

393
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,090
and sure enough, it...

394
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,610
Get out of here!

395
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:10,970
Mr. Zan.

396
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,790
Why are you just standing there?

397
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,250
Get out!

398
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:15,590
Go, go, go.

399
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:22,860
Chief Zhao.

400
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,140
Captain Qi.

401
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:25,510
What era

402
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,920
