428
00:20:45,420 --> 00:20:47,380
Mr. Zan, how about we go eat?

429
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,450
Alright.

430
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:50,360
What did you eat last night?

431
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,500
Last night, I had bread soaked in soup.

432
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:53,500
It is delicious.

433
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:54,450
It's great.

434
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:57,680
So are we having it again tonight?

435
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,410
I'm not having it.

436
00:20:59,410 --> 00:21:01,400
Tonight, we can have lamp soup.

437
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:02,070
Alright.

438
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:05,790
Mr. Zan didn't even ask
what you wanted to eat.

439
00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:07,450
Luo Qing.

440
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,860
What do you think I want to say?

441
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:12,860
Mr. Zan wanted to say that

442
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:14,890
the paper mentions

443
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,980
that during the Western Jin,

444
00:21:17,130 --> 00:21:19,440
the Zi Mausoleum
and Du Mausoleum were robbed.

445
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:20,790
But we can't just assume

446
00:21:20,810 --> 00:21:23,450
the black pottery figurines
came from one of them.

447
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:24,240
Maybe other emperor mausoleums

448
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,340
were also robbed during the Western Jin,

449
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:28,540
but they weren't recorded in the paper.

450
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,400
I just wanted to say,

451
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,570
we shouldn't make assumptions

452
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,110
