459
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:50,970
What we fear most is

460
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:53,880
interpreting history
with subjective judgment.

461
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,840
You eat one bite at a time,

462
00:21:57,520 --> 00:21:59,190
you walk one step at a time.

463
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:00,810
I know you're smart,

464
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:03,980
