lead to mistakes.

465
00:22:05,970 --> 00:22:06,650
Mr. Zan.

466
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:08,880
We understand our mistake.

467
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:10,300
Right, we understand.

468
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:10,830
Alright.

469
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,040
Think about it

470
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:14,560
