471
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:17,000
Write a self-reflection.

472
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,400
Leave.

473
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:18,480
Okay.

474
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:33,400
Tang,

