567
00:25:44,590 --> 00:25:46,910
besides me, there are only 3 people left.

568
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:48,740
Du Mausoleum is close,

569
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:50,310
a patrol takes three hours.

570
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,960
Zi Mausoleum's farther, 40 miles away.

571
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,820
It takes me two hours to ride a bike

572
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:56,570
from here to Zi Mausoleum.

573
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:57,360
Besides,

574
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,680
Zi Mausoleum isn't just one tomb.

575
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:01,160
It's a big area.

576
00:26:01,690 --> 00:26:02,960
If I patrol the whole area,

577
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:03,890
it takes 6 hours.

578
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:09,230
I know the difficulties.

579
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,750
But knowing isn't enough, Captain Yang.

580
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:14,020
You need to help us solve the problem.

581
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,880
Forget about the person,

582
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,640
let's talk about this bicycle.

583
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:20,510
I've already worn out two this year.

584
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,200
No funds to replace them.

585
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:24,270
Director Wu brought his own bicycle.

586
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,020
He even had an argument
with his family over it.

587
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:28,400
Don't talk about the difficulties anymore.

588
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:30,070
I've been listening for a while.

589
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:30,720
The patrol

590
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,830
at Zi Mausoleum

591
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:34,880
is inadequate.

592
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:35,830
Now,

593
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:38,470
there's a possibility

594
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:41,350
of a case at
Nan Mausoleum and Dou Mausoleum.

595
00:26:41,350 --> 00:26:44,030
These two are near the village.

596
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:47,110
If something happens,

597
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,640
the villagers will definitely notice.

598
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:51,000
I don't agree with that.

599
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:52,920
The villagers are busy,

600
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,940
they're not here to watch the Mausoleums.

601
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:56,900
Besides, this is your job.

602
00:26:57,160 --> 00:26:59,690
Who says we're only relying on
the villagers?

603
00:26:59,930 --> 00:27:01,110
We have volunteered cultural relic

604
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:03,240
conservators at Yin Village.

605
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:04,790
They're dedicated and responsible.

606
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:05,920
I'm from Yin Village.

607
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:06,520
Which one?

608
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,080
You're from Yin Village.

609
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:10,010
A bachelor in your village,

610
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:12,240
named Yan Shoucun.

611
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:13,160
What?

612
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:15,790
Don't talk about
asking him to watch the Mausoleum.

613
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,250
If you tore down his house,

614
00:27:17,510 --> 00:27:19,240
he'd probably not even notice.

615
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:20,110
Captain Qi.

616
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:22,830
Right now, it's good
if we can even find anyone.

617
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:23,560
Yan Shoucun?

618
00:27:23,870 --> 00:27:24,600
Yan Shoucun.

619
00:27:31,190 --> 00:27:32,190
You little thief!

620
00:27:34,810 --> 00:27:37,210
Little thief!
I've been waiting for you for ages!

621
00:27:37,210 --> 00:27:38,240
What are you doing?

622
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:38,750
Stop being stubborn.

623
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,750
Who's the little thief here?

624
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:41,200
I knew something was off
with you during the Shehuo.

625
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:41,550
What?

626
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:42,880
You're here again today?

627
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,800
-I've had enough of you.
-Stop shouting.

628
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,240
If you keep shouting,
I'll stuff your mouth.

629
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,240
Come on, tie me up.

630
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:47,770
Stop shouting.

631
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:48,230
What...

632
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,110
Open your mouth.

633
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:50,440
Are you going to open it?

634
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,080
Still not opening it?

635
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:55,340
Come on, get up.

636
00:27:55,780 --> 00:27:56,210
Get up!

637
00:27:57,070 --> 00:27:58,130
You get up and walk!

638
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,450
Walk!

639
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:06,160
What's the progress

640
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,650
on the Wulingyuan's investigation?

641
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:09,720
I've been with Captain Yang's team,

642
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,240
and we've gone through nine Mausoleums.

643
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,240
They all say there are no looting pits.

644
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,440
What do you mean?

645
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:16,090
You can't just listen with your ears,

646
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:18,500
you have to see with your own eyes.

647
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:19,760
We've seen them.

648
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,550
You have no idea how many glares

649
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:23,750
we've gotten these past couple of days.

650
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:25,750
Everyone thinks
we're coming to cause trouble.

651
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,030
If it weren't for Captain Yang,

652
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:29,430
no one would've
even bothered to talk to us.

653
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,750
It's the same with me.

654
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,750
I'm hated by everyone now.

655
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:35,970
Captain Qi.

656
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:39,260
Chief Zhao wants you to come over.

657
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:39,650
Go!

658
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:41,510
Go, didn't you hear?

659
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:42,730
Hurry up.

660
00:28:43,080 --> 00:28:43,870
Youliang.

661
00:28:44,150 --> 00:28:44,950
Come on, move.

662
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:45,910
Move.

663
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:49,160
Youliang. I've got the little thief!

664
00:28:49,490 --> 00:28:50,420
The tomb raider.

665
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:51,310
Look.

666
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:53,740
What little thief?

667
00:28:55,570 --> 00:28:57,530
This guy didn't bring any tools with him.

668
00:28:57,530 --> 00:28:58,350
How's he a tomb raider?

669
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:59,490
Shehuo...

670
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,810
I've been watching him since Shehuo.

671
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:03,480
Today,

672
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,560
I saw him on the plain,

673
00:29:04,560 --> 00:29:05,430
Riding a bike,

674
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,190
he kept circling around Dou Mausoleum.

675
00:29:07,190 --> 00:29:08,490
You take that towel off him.

676
00:29:08,490 --> 00:29:09,570
L-Let him speak.

677
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:10,010
No!

678
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:10,940
What's your meaning?

679
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:12,800
You trying to steal my credit now?

680
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,950
Hurry up and call Qi Dacang!

681
00:29:15,130 --> 00:29:15,770
Tell him to come.

682
00:29:15,770 --> 00:29:17,770
If he doesn't come, I'm not leaving.

683
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:18,960
You fool.

684
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,640
You went to
the Relics Protection Institute

685
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,970
to order people around?

686
00:29:24,750 --> 00:29:25,680
What's going on?

687
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:27,520
Did Director Tang complain?

688
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:31,310
Not doing real work, but quick at this.

689
00:29:31,570 --> 00:29:33,230
You're too straightforward.

690
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:36,370
What were you supposed to do here?

691
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:38,750
To investigate, to make inquiries.

692
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,720
Not to lecture people.

693
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,860
They didn't patrol once a week

694
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,440
for Nan Mausoleum and Dou Mausoleum.

695
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:47,640
No wonder they can't stop tomb raiders.

696
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:49,240
You're annoying.

697
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,070
Director Tang told you.

698
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,590
They have their own difficulties.

699
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:55,640
His difficulties? Right now,
the hardest thing is for us police.

700
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,640
I checked around,

701
00:29:57,030 --> 00:29:58,350
his problems are the biggest.

702
00:29:58,350 --> 00:29:59,590
How dare he

703
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,110
come to complain?

704
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,640
Send me a few men,

705
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:05,920
I'll handle it myself.

706
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:06,720
Let him see

707
00:30:07,310 --> 00:30:08,110
how it's done.

708
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:10,790
Can't you see

709
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:12,390
how busy the whole bureau is?

710
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,590
You think I'm

711
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:15,270
some kind of magician?

712
00:30:15,270 --> 00:30:17,510
Just snap my fingers and
have people appear out of thin air?

713
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:19,350
Yeah, sure, you're quite the expert.

714
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:20,550
Stop sucking up to me.

715
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,720
I'm a cow, you can't butter me up.

716
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:23,840
And besides,

717
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:26,290
you don't know how big Bailu Plain is.

718
00:30:26,290 --> 00:30:28,220
It's not a job for just a few people.

719
00:30:32,550 --> 00:30:34,080
Fine, I'm coming right now.

720
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,200
To catch a tomb raider.

721
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:35,590
Go.

722
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,660
I just brewed some new tea.

723
00:30:39,550 --> 00:30:40,550
It's good tea.

724
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:43,900
Save me some.

725
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,660
Alright, I'm talking to you.

726
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:47,100
No, stay put.

727
00:30:47,930 --> 00:30:50,170
I won't let you run away.

728
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:52,510
What's going on with you?

729
00:30:52,590 --> 00:30:54,830
How long's it been
since you washed that towel,?

730
00:30:54,830 --> 00:30:56,520
You're gonna suffocate the guy.

731
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:58,030
Dacang hasn't even come yet
and you've already messed up.

732
00:30:58,030 --> 00:30:58,960
I don't want to talk to you.

733
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,400
I'll wait for Dacang to get here.

734
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:01,160
Then I'll talk to him.

735
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:02,020
You usually act all dumb,

736
00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:03,720
but now you think you're someone?

737
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:04,770
You think you're someone now?

738
00:31:04,770 --> 00:31:06,400
When something happens,
can you take responsibility?

739
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,270
I can. I can.

740
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,590
What's going on?

741
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:09,300
What's going on here?

742
00:31:09,300 --> 00:31:09,790
Dacang,

743
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:11,750
I've caught the tomb raider.

744
00:31:11,750 --> 00:31:13,550
-What are you doing?
-Do you see?

745
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:16,920
This guy is a graduate student
from Qinbei University.

746
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:18,240
He's studying archaeology.

747
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,000
Look! Look! Look!

748
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:19,830
Did you hear that?

749
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:21,310
He's a graduate student
from Qinbei University.

750
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,200
He's studying archaeology.

751
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,160
He came here to do archaeology.

752
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,030
What little thief?

753
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:25,880
I don't care if he's
Monk Tang or Monk Sha.

754
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:27,880
He's just a little thief.

755
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:29,440
Sorry about that.

756
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:30,900
Hey, kid, you alright?

757
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:33,780
Give me some water.

758
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:34,480
Wait here.

759
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:37,340
Dacang.

760
00:31:38,150 --> 00:31:39,020
Do you recognize him?

761
00:31:39,020 --> 00:31:40,820
What are you messing around for?

762
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,170
Alright, alright.

763
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:55,540
Why'd you suddenly come to the plain?

764
00:31:57,330 --> 00:31:59,190
Helping you find the looting pit?

765
00:32:02,210 --> 00:32:03,610
That's the police's job.

766
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:06,580
You're just a graduate student.

767
00:32:07,350 --> 00:32:09,410
Why are you getting involved in this?

768
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,830
I just want to prove that

769
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,070
my guess is right.

770
00:32:15,570 --> 00:32:17,630
Are you arguing with your professor?

771
00:32:18,930 --> 00:32:20,210
Argue with him?

772
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:22,440
T-this is an academic debate, you know?

773
00:32:22,950 --> 00:32:24,590
If I can't find it at Zi Mausoleum.

774
00:32:24,590 --> 00:32:26,190
I'll move on to Du Mausoleum.

775
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:27,550
Right, right.

776
00:32:27,850 --> 00:32:29,250
Don't say anything more.

777
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:30,610
-Uncle.
-Let me tell you,

778
00:32:30,610 --> 00:32:32,270
if Dacang hadn't come in time,

779
00:32:32,700 --> 00:32:35,360
we wouldn't know
what to do with this situation.

780
00:32:36,870 --> 00:32:40,040
Tonight, I'll have your aunt make the kid
a bowl of oil-splashed noodles.

781
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,770
That's our way of apologizing.

782
00:32:42,810 --> 00:32:43,210
Uncle.

783
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:47,120
I'm investigating a tomb raiding case,

784
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:49,030
so I can't go into details.

785
00:32:50,410 --> 00:32:51,720
I just want to ask,

786
00:32:52,190 --> 00:32:55,190
have you heard of any looting pit
around Zi Mausoleum?

787
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:57,350
Zi Mausoleum.

788
00:32:57,370 --> 00:32:58,770
Go ask at Phoenix Mountain.

789
00:32:58,770 --> 00:33:00,810
It's about two or three miles
away from here.

790
00:33:00,810 --> 00:33:01,960
How would I know about things there?

791
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:02,400
No.

792
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,300
I'm talking about Zi Mausoleum.

793
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:07,730
It's not just the tomb
of Emperor Taizong of Han.

794
00:33:07,730 --> 00:33:08,210
What?

795
00:33:09,610 --> 00:33:12,540
Zi Mausoleum isn't
the tomb of Emperor Taizong of Han.

796
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:13,400
Then what is it?

797
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,670
Well, the Zi Mausoleum

798
00:33:15,700 --> 00:33:17,600
we're talking about is actually a broad concept.

799
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,310
It includes Emperor Taizong of Han's tomb,

800
00:33:19,310 --> 00:33:21,270
as well as the tomb of Empress Dowager Bo

801
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:22,400
and Dou Mausoleum.

802
00:33:24,410 --> 00:33:24,880
Then,

803
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:28,200
our place is closer to Dou Mausoleum.

804
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:31,990
But I haven't heard of
any looting pits around there.

805
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:33,470
Uncle,

806
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:36,010
can you find someone

807
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:38,160
to help get the bike back for him?

808
00:33:38,890 --> 00:33:39,420
Alright,

809
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:40,890
small stuff.

810
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:41,500
I'll go.

811
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,160
-Here, take this.
-Good.

812
00:33:43,330 --> 00:33:44,090
The blue one.

813
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:45,110
Alright, the blue one.

814
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,310
Thank you, thank you.

815
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:08,710
Fang,

816
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,960
what are you looking at?

817
00:34:11,030 --> 00:34:12,840
I'm looking at this photo...

818
00:34:14,170 --> 00:34:16,429
That's my dad and my great-grandfather.

819
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:18,880
It doesn't look like them.

820
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:19,810
What do you mean?

821
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,960
They'll look more alike
as they grow older.

822
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:22,310
Bro,

823
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:23,469
have some water.

824
00:34:23,469 --> 00:34:24,800
Alright, thanks.
You go about your business.

825
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,860
No need to thank me.

826
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:40,920
Where's Heisa?

827
00:34:41,050 --> 00:34:41,590
Lost.

828
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:44,540
Bro, how dare you ask?

829
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:47,020
Heisa got lost during Shehuo.

830
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:49,010
I told you about it already,

831
00:34:49,010 --> 00:34:50,139
and you didn't care.

832
00:34:51,260 --> 00:34:52,400
It's been so long.

833
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,639
Heisa still hasn't come back.

834
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:56,280
Still hasn't returned?

835
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:57,400
Yes.

836
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,670
You.

837
00:34:58,690 --> 00:34:59,570
I told you,

838
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,560
it might be lost.

839
00:35:00,710 --> 00:35:01,360
No way.

840
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:03,050
Heisa is clever.

841
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,110
During Shehuo,

842
00:35:05,810 --> 00:35:07,540
I heard it barking in the field.

843
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:08,960
Then I ran into two people.

844
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:11,440
They looked suspicious,
